title.value: Collection of documents on annexations to Menlo Park, California and the incorporation of East Palo Alto, California

note.value: Collection of photocopies of municipal, as well as some county and state documents regarding the annexation of unicorporated lands to Menlo Park, California. Also included is a set of documents regarding the incorporation of East Palo Alto, California.
